<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="content-wrapper wrapper--narrow split">

    <div class="split-left">
      <h2>Deep‑Tech Advisory & Venture Building</h2>

      <p>
        Organizations often make promising discoveries in R&D but lack the clarity to turn them into viable products.
        VAIRA bridges this gap with deep engineering expertise and hands‑on founder experience.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Structured evaluation</strong> of technology maturity, capabilities, and risks</li>
        <li><strong>Clear development pathways</strong> from lab insight to commercial prototype</li>
        <li><strong>Supplier and prototyping guidance</strong> to accelerate early execution</li>
        <li><strong>Capability building</strong> through embedded coaching and technical leadership</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="split-right">
      <div class="micro-illustration">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="260" height="260" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 260 260"><g stroke-width="3"><path stroke="currentColor" d="M40 138h55v55H40z"/><path fill="var(--primary-light)" stroke="currentColor" d="M70 81h55v55H70z"/><path stroke="currentColor" d="M100 24h55v55h-55z"/><path stroke="var(--primary)" d="M158 24h49v119h50v50h-99Z"/></g></svg>

      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
        <strong><em>Case Example:</em></strong> A university‑affiliated team developed a novel materials processing technology.
        VAIRA defined a TRL‑based plan, identified suppliers, and supported early market analysis - accelerating their path toward commercialization.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>


